20018000.text: Welcome, Sohyeop!\nIt's an honor to be able to deliver such good news.

20018001.text: Nothing else, we have prepared a new match \nto follow the unfortunate end of the Martial Arts Competition for a Happy New Year!!

20018002.text: Named <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>Half-moon dance</>!\nCompared to the Martial Arts Competition for a good harvest, the process and reward method have been changed.

20018003.text: There is just one place left, so please participate~\nThe rules are the same as in the martial arts competition, you just have to win the match with your opponent!

20018004.text: If you <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>win</> in a match, you will get a <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>good reward</>,

20018006.text: How do you feel? A new event that will be the new face of the new Daeeobangchungta!\nIsn't it interesting?

20018007.text: (It's very interesting and he wants to participate right away.)

20018008.text: Okay! If you've decided, worrying about it any more is a waste!\nThen prepare your mind and enter!

20018010.text: (Apply to participate in the half-moon dance.)

20018011.text: You can participate in the next match right away!\nNow, let's enter!
